Cyberpunk style: A towering holographic control hub floats in the center of a neon-drenched command room, with dozens of glowing data streams in electric blue, magenta, and amber spiraling inward from all directions like rivers of light. A solitary figure stands at a curved console, their silhouette backlit by the swirling vortex of incoming signals, one hand raised to redirect and filter the streams into organized channels that flow outward through different portals. The room pulses with energy as notification orbs of varying sizes and urgency colors queue in orbital rings around the central hub, waiting to be sorted. Rain streaks down massive windows revealing a sprawling megacity below, its towers dotted with blinking communication arrays.
